OL,3,CThe Welsh dad who lost his son at 27
OL,4,Cand now helps bereaved families
OL,6,FA foundation set up to honour the life
OL,7,Fof a much-loved son from Ammanford has
OL,8,Fbeen chosen to run a national service
OL,9,Fto help families whose loved ones have
OL,10,Ftaken their own lives.
OL,12,FFive years ago, Jesse Lewis' life
OL,13,Fchanged forever when his son Jac took
OL,14,Fhis own life at just 27-years-old.
OL,16,FJesse set up the Jac Lewis Foundation
OL,17,Fin an effort to help others in the
OL,18,FSwansea and Ammanford areas who are
OL,19,Fstruggling with their mental health or
OL,20,Fhave experienced a loved one taking
OL,21,Ftheir own life.
