OL,3,CThe Welsh dad who lost his son at 27
OL,4,Cand now helps bereaved families
OL,6,F"No one thinks it's going to happen,"
OL,7,FJesse told ITV Cymru Wales. "No one
OL,8,Fdoes. But you need to understand that
OL,9,Fit's a possibility. Get that help
OL,10,Fwhile you can."
OL,12,FEarlier this week the Welsh Government
OL,13,Fis launched a national advice service
OL,14,Faimed at supporting all those affected
OL,15,Fby suicide which will be run by the
OL,16,FJac Lewis Foundation, and new guidance
OL,17,Ffor agencies and organisations.
