OL,3,CThe Welsh dad who lost his son at 27
OL,4,Cand now helps bereaved families
OL,6,FThen new service comes as the latest
OL,7,FONS data shows a rise in the number of
OL,8,Fpeople in Wales dying by suicide, with
OL,9,Faround one person a day taking their
OL,10,Fown life.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government say the new
OL,13,Fservice will ensure anyone in Wales
OL,14,Fwho has been affected can receive
OL,15,Fimmediate sensitive and compassionate
OL,16,Fsupport, including regular contact
OL,17,Ffrom a dedicated liaison officer for
OL,18,Fas long as needed, and support to
OL,19,Faccess wider services.
