OL,3,CThe Welsh dad who lost his son at 27
OL,4,Cand now helps bereaved families
OL,6,F"The National Advisory and Liaison
OL,7,Fservice will be an invaluable first
OL,8,Fport of call for those who have been
OL,9,Faffected by suicide and will provide
OL,10,Fvital support to individuals and
OL,11,Ffamilies of all ages in Wales as they
OL,12,Fnavigate their way through the process.
OL,14,F"This guidance will help organisations
OL,15,Fbetter understand their role in
OL,16,Fsupporting people bereaved or affected
OL,17,Fby suicide.
