OL,4,Cand now helps bereaved families
OL,6,F"We want to ensure all those who are
OL,7,Faffected receive timely, compassionate
OL,8,Fand effective support where and when
OL,9,Fthey need it.
OL,11,F"Through the ongoing development and
OL,12,Fimplementation of our Suicide and Self-
OL,13,Fharm Prevention Strategy we will
OL,14,Fexplore what more can be done to
OL,15,Fprevent suicide in Wales."
