OL,6,FLiz Thomas-Evans, chief executive
OL,7,Fofficer of the Jac Lewis Foundation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are profoundly grateful for
OL,9,Fthe opportunity to deliver the
OL,10,FNational Advisory and Liaison Service
OL,11,Fin Wales.
OL,13,F"This service will ensure critical
OL,14,Fsupport is available to individuals
OL,15,Fand families throughout Wales who have
OL,16,Fbeen affected by suicide, working with
OL,17,Fother bereavement services to provide
OL,18,Fthe essential support, guidance, and
OL,19,Fresources they need during their most
OL,20,Fdifficult times.
